article_title: Walgreen Will Retain Its Growth Momentum In Q3'14

article_metadata.author: Great Speculations

og.description: The company retained it growth momentum in Q3 2014, as is evident from strong sales for the quarter (reported on June 5). Total sales for Q3 2014 were $19.47 billion, 6.4% higher compared to Q3 2013.
